WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:00.830 --> 00:00:07.300
<i>The war between the Imperial Army and the 
Hellhorde has raged on for many years...</i>

3
00:00:08.940 --> 00:00:17.290
<i>In the midst of battle, the Princess and 
Commander of the Imperial Third Legion</i>

4
00:00:17.290 --> 00:00:20.240
<i>falls into the hands of the Hellhorde.</i>

5
00:00:20.760 --> 00:00:25.830
<i>The Hellhorde, seeking to extract 
Imperial secrets from the princess...</i>

6
00:00:26.290 --> 00:00:33.070
<i>...mercilessly subjects her 
to torture day after day.</i>

7
00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:47.310
Torture Tortura, at your service.

8
00:00:50.050 --> 00:00:52.700
The location of the 
empire's ultimate weapon.

9
00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:54.980
The days when security is lax.

10
00:00:54.980 --> 00:00:57.370
Their secret military code.

11
00:00:57.370 --> 00:00:59.740
All utterly worthless.

12
00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:05.700
You haven't managed to get any useful 
information out of the princess.

13
00:01:06.810 --> 00:01:10.710
Could it be that you've lost your touch?

14
00:01:11.560 --> 00:01:14.100
No, I dare say not.

15
00:01:14.380 --> 00:01:21.260
I could strip you of your title 
of grand inquisitor right here.

16
00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:23.400
But I'll offer you a chance.

17
00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:27.490
Have a stab at torturing me.

18
00:01:29.770 --> 00:01:31.370
Y-Your Majesty!

19
00:01:31.370 --> 00:01:32.820
I can't allow that!

20
00:01:35.190 --> 00:01:37.350
We will begin in one hour.

21
00:01:37.350 --> 00:01:39.870
I'll see if you have what it takes.

22
00:01:39.870 --> 00:01:44.040
And I think it should be 
clear what will happen...

23
00:01:44.410 --> 00:01:46.780
if you disappoint me.

24
00:01:48.550 --> 00:01:49.380
Yes.

25
00:02:06.180 --> 00:02:13.520
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

26
00:03:23.820 --> 00:03:28.320
'Tis time for torture, Your Majesty.

27
00:03:28.320 --> 00:03:30.140
Geh-heh-heh.

28
00:03:30.620 --> 00:03:32.650
<i>Torturing His Majesty?</i>

29
00:03:32.650 --> 00:03:33.660
<i>How foolhardy!</i>

30
00:03:34.710 --> 00:03:37.890
<i>His Majesty stands above all of demonkind.</i>

31
00:03:37.890 --> 00:03:40.030
<i>His mental resilience is far above average!</i>

32
00:03:40.030 --> 00:03:41.630
<i>What exactly does she have planned?</i>

33
00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:49.750
I shall be using this for 
today's torture session.

34
00:03:52.930 --> 00:03:54.150
'Tis beer.

35
00:03:54.150 --> 00:03:55.860
Geh-heh-heh.

36
00:03:55.860 --> 00:03:59.800
You should cater your torture 
method to your victim.

37
00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:01.430
<i>It's not working on him!</i>

38
00:04:01.430 --> 00:04:08.050
I enjoy a drink every night with the queen in 
the privacy of my home, and you offer me beer?

39
00:04:08.430 --> 00:04:09.840
Not a bad choice!

40
00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:10.930
<i>It's not?!</i>

41
00:04:11.770 --> 00:04:14.560
However, you stand before the Hell-Lord.

42
00:04:15.060 --> 00:04:18.590
I've sampled the finest alcoholic 
beverages across the lands.

43
00:04:18.590 --> 00:04:24.340
Do you think you can defeat me 
with that low-brow canned beer?

44
00:04:27.070 --> 00:04:28.690
<i>It's totally working!</i>

45
00:04:29.030 --> 00:04:30.990
'Tis but canned beer.

46
00:04:30.990 --> 00:04:33.080
Yet 'tis mighty indeed.

47
00:04:33.080 --> 00:04:37.170
Your Majesty, do you know the 
tastiest way to pour a can of beer?

48
00:04:37.580 --> 00:04:40.430
The tastiest way?

49
00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:42.880
First, when pouring it into the glass...

50
00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:48.100
As you begin, immediately raise 
the can as high as you can.

51
00:04:49.660 --> 00:04:53.030
If you do that, you'll get nothing but foam!

52
00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:55.090
That is fine.

53
00:04:55.780 --> 00:04:58.450
That is what we want.

54
00:04:59.610 --> 00:05:03.400
Once it reaches the very top, 
we wait for the head to settle.

55
00:05:03.760 --> 00:05:09.480
A vigorous pour results in fine bubbles 
that become compacted even further.

56
00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:16.130
Once the head is stable, slowly pour 
in beer from the rim of the glass.

57
00:05:17.550 --> 00:05:22.130
Finally, once you've poured enough that 
the foam covers the top of the glass...

58
00:05:24.790 --> 00:05:26.600
'Tis complete.

59
00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:28.090
Wha—?!

60
00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:33.300
J-Just look at this fluffy foam...

61
00:05:33.300 --> 00:05:36.180
No, <i>fluffoam</i>!

62
00:05:36.180 --> 00:05:37.600
<i>He gave it a name!</i>

63
00:05:38.100 --> 00:05:41.760
A far cry from the flaccid head 
you get from pouring mindlessly!

64
00:05:41.760 --> 00:05:44.820
It stands out like a 
dollop of whipped cream!

65
00:05:44.820 --> 00:05:47.940
Fluffoam! Fluffoam!

66
00:05:47.940 --> 00:05:49.470
<i>Is he pleased with himself for that?</i>

67
00:05:57.410 --> 00:05:58.470
Your Majesty!

68
00:05:59.470 --> 00:06:00.830
<i>It can't be!</i>

69
00:06:00.830 --> 00:06:02.640
<i>To think that I...</i>

70
00:06:03.260 --> 00:06:06.120
<i>would tremble with temptation!</i>

71
00:06:06.500 --> 00:06:08.640
Please endure it, Your Majesty!

72
00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:15.010
Even when you faced the Hero, strongest 
soldier in the Imperial Army, in a duel,

73
00:06:15.010 --> 00:06:19.170
you shrugged off all of 
his attacks, held firm,

74
00:06:19.850 --> 00:06:21.430
and came out standing strong!

75
00:06:21.430 --> 00:06:23.650
You are the pinnacle of all demonkind!

76
00:06:23.650 --> 00:06:25.180
The strongest monster of all!

77
00:06:25.740 --> 00:06:27.340
The Hell-Lord himself!

78
00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:28.070
The Hell-Lord himself

79
00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:31.860
Your Majesty!

80
00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:34.350
Y-Your Majesty?

81
00:06:34.750 --> 00:06:35.450
Heh.

82
00:06:36.020 --> 00:06:37.240
That's right.

83
00:06:38.040 --> 00:06:40.140
I am the Hell-Lord.

84
00:06:40.630 --> 00:06:47.090
This torture is nothing to me!

85
00:06:47.580 --> 00:06:50.290
Incidentally, this beer 
with the fluffy foam...

86
00:06:50.290 --> 00:06:53.140
or rather, this fluffoam beer...

87
00:06:53.390 --> 00:06:56.430
The longer you wait, the 
more foam will dissipate.

88
00:06:57.810 --> 00:07:00.280
'Tis best to enjoy it 
immediately after pouring.

89
00:07:00.280 --> 00:07:04.970
My weakness is light magic!

90
00:07:04.120 --> 00:07:06.050
He gave it away!

91
00:07:06.610 --> 00:07:09.320
The Hell-Lord
confessed

92
00:07:10.190 --> 00:07:11.280
Enjoy.

93
00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:12.390
Yes.

94
00:07:18.710 --> 00:07:23.150
<i>It's so light, with a creamy mouthfeel 
that's downright criminal.</i>

95
00:07:23.150 --> 00:07:27.960
<i>And the golden nectar of life 
blanketed in fluffoam...</i>

96
00:07:27.960 --> 00:07:30.510
<i>rushes through my body!</i>

97
00:07:32.010 --> 00:07:35.140
<i>So divine, it's like my throat is in heaven!</i>

98
00:07:36.900 --> 00:07:40.790
<i>Foam fizzing like herald angels singing!</i>

99
00:07:41.090 --> 00:07:44.780
<i>I'm filled with joy!</i>

100
00:07:48.990 --> 00:07:52.940
This is no mere canned beer!

101
00:07:53.340 --> 00:07:55.690
It's light magic!

102
00:07:55.690 --> 00:07:58.920
His Majesty is being purified!

103
00:07:59.620 --> 00:08:02.380
<i>Don't drink until you come of age.</i>

104
00:08:03.960 --> 00:08:06.130
Grand
Inquisitor's
Chamber

105
00:08:06.500 --> 00:08:10.300
His Majesty granted me permission 
to continue the torture.

106
00:08:11.310 --> 00:08:16.070
But I must admit that as it stands, the 
intelligence we can gain is limited in scope.

107
00:08:17.350 --> 00:08:19.820
I suppose I could try something different.

108
00:08:23.310 --> 00:08:27.310
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

109
00:08:23.630 --> 00:08:25.510
<i>Fluffoam...</i>

110
00:08:34.740 --> 00:08:35.780
Princess.

111
00:08:36.730 --> 00:08:38.620
'Tis time for torture.

112
00:08:38.830 --> 00:08:42.380
We'll be trying something 
a little different today.

113
00:08:43.770 --> 00:08:46.220
It doesn't matter what 
torture you throw at us.

114
00:08:46.510 --> 00:08:48.120
I'm sure Her Highness will spill the beans.

115
00:08:48.120 --> 00:08:49.210
What?!

116
00:08:49.410 --> 00:08:53.680
<i>Did Ex's faith in me plummet 
thanks to my constant slip-ups?!</i>

117
00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:55.390
Just you wait, Ex!

118
00:08:55.390 --> 00:08:57.360
Today's the day I finally resist!

119
00:08:57.360 --> 00:08:57.790
Hmph.

120
00:08:57.790 --> 00:08:58.800
What?!

121
00:08:59.250 --> 00:09:02.390
I shan't be torturing you today, Princess.

122
00:09:02.650 --> 00:09:03.590
What?

123
00:09:03.590 --> 00:09:04.690
Please come in.

124
00:09:06.470 --> 00:09:08.460
Weaponsmith Gilga-chan.

125
00:09:08.310 --> 00:09:10.480
Weaponsmith, Pain-Private
Gilga

126
00:09:08.460 --> 00:09:10.470
Hey there.

127
00:09:10.470 --> 00:09:12.250
A weaponsmith?

128
00:09:13.210 --> 00:09:15.180
Aw, man.

129
00:09:15.180 --> 00:09:18.130
Hey! Stop that! Not there!

130
00:09:15.180 --> 00:09:19.450
Being stuck here has left 
you in awful condition.

131
00:09:18.740 --> 00:09:19.450
Cut it out!

132
00:09:19.820 --> 00:09:20.780
Yes.

133
00:09:19.830 --> 00:09:22.850
Don't touch me! Hey! Stop!

134
00:09:20.780 --> 00:09:23.860
Sacred Blade Ex, today we'll be...

135
00:09:22.850 --> 00:09:26.010
Hands off! Hey! I said stop!

136
00:09:24.250 --> 00:09:25.990
torturing you instead.

137
00:09:28.500 --> 00:09:29.860
Don't underestimate me.

138
00:09:30.440 --> 00:09:32.640
I am Ex, the sacred blade.

139
00:09:33.250 --> 00:09:36.990
In my long service to the royal family, 
alongside generations of noble knights,

140
00:09:36.990 --> 00:09:39.700
I've braved a countless number of battles.

141
00:09:40.750 --> 00:09:44.660
I would never submit to 
any means of torture!

142
00:09:44.660 --> 00:09:45.700
Alrighty.

143
00:09:45.700 --> 00:09:47.980
Hey! Unhand me!

144
00:09:46.650 --> 00:09:49.140
Let's start by taking off this surface rust.

145
00:09:47.980 --> 00:09:49.530
I'm a sacred blade, you know!

146
00:09:59.730 --> 00:10:00.900
Ex?

147
00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:02.840
You've got it wrong, Your Highness!

148
00:10:02.840 --> 00:10:04.230
That was a battle cry!

149
00:10:04.230 --> 00:10:06.290
I was letting out a manly battle cry!

150
00:10:06.290 --> 00:10:07.910
It wasn't because of any 
pleasure I felt at all!

151
00:10:07.910 --> 00:10:08.990
I simply let out a battle cry!

152
00:10:08.990 --> 00:10:10.250
All sacred blades would do the same!

153
00:10:10.250 --> 00:10:12.000
I'm definitely not the only 
one who'd cry out...

154
00:10:10.660 --> 00:10:12.000
Slow down.

155
00:10:14.050 --> 00:10:16.750
Next, I'll use this rotary grindstone...

156
00:10:17.010 --> 00:10:20.080
and sharpen you real nice and gentle.

157
00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:30.690
<i>What a refreshing shave.</i>

158
00:10:30.900 --> 00:10:33.700
<i>And the perfect level of sharpening!</i>

159
00:10:34.970 --> 00:10:36.160
<i>I can feel it.</i>

160
00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:39.140
<i>I don't need to test out my blade to tell.</i>

161
00:10:40.770 --> 00:10:44.830
<i>While retaining the bashing force a 
sword needs to smash through armor...</i>

162
00:10:46.270 --> 00:10:50.400
<i>it boasts the sharp edge of a 
katana to cut through flesh!</i>

163
00:10:51.100 --> 00:10:52.910
<i>I am a sacred blade!</i>

164
00:10:52.910 --> 00:10:57.430
<i>The sacred blade Ex!</i>

165
00:10:57.880 --> 00:10:58.960
Ex!

166
00:10:58.960 --> 00:11:00.300
Ex, snap out of it!

167
00:11:01.180 --> 00:11:02.350
Ex!

168
00:11:04.250 --> 00:11:06.430
It's okay, Your Highness.

169
00:11:07.010 --> 00:11:08.980
I admit that felt good.

170
00:11:08.980 --> 00:11:12.390
However, I feel no obligation 
to share my secrets!

171
00:11:12.390 --> 00:11:14.930
I will endure this torture!

172
00:11:14.930 --> 00:11:16.100
Great!

173
00:11:16.100 --> 00:11:17.350
I'm impressed, Ex!

174
00:11:17.350 --> 00:11:19.600
I would have spilled the 
beans three times by now!

175
00:11:19.600 --> 00:11:20.550
Your Highness?

176
00:11:21.020 --> 00:11:24.460
Well, that's a shame, but it 
looks like I'm done here.

177
00:11:25.300 --> 00:11:28.680
Y-You've still only done a 
coarse pass over my surface!

178
00:11:28.680 --> 00:11:29.750
I know.

179
00:11:29.750 --> 00:11:32.740
I'd love to give you the 
full treatment as well.

180
00:11:33.130 --> 00:11:36.120
But this is supposed to be torture.

181
00:11:37.310 --> 00:11:40.770
Well, if you were to reveal a secret...

182
00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:43.290
I wouldn't mind giving you a nice finish.

183
00:11:44.330 --> 00:11:45.760
Ex...

184
00:11:45.760 --> 00:11:47.880
Rest assured, Your Highness.

185
00:11:48.630 --> 00:11:50.970
I am the sacred blade Ex.

186
00:11:50.970 --> 00:11:52.320
Your trusty sword.

187
00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:56.220
I wouldn't dare act out of 
my own personal interest.

188
00:11:56.220 --> 00:11:57.740
Ex!

189
00:11:57.740 --> 00:12:00.510
Getting polished up with 
a nice, sharp edge...

190
00:12:01.250 --> 00:12:03.670
That would benefit Your Highness as well!

191
00:12:03.670 --> 00:12:05.980
Ex!

192
00:12:07.040 --> 00:12:08.750
Okay, let's finish you up!

193
00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:11.910
Ex confessed

194
00:12:17.880 --> 00:12:19.210
I see.

195
00:12:19.810 --> 00:12:22.990
So the Demon Sword Murasa and 
Fire Sword Amon are lovers.

196
00:12:23.640 --> 00:12:25.880
Magnificent! I feel superb!

197
00:12:25.880 --> 00:12:30.250
Glare...

198
00:12:35.230 --> 00:12:37.690
U-Um...

199
00:12:37.940 --> 00:12:40.720
Your Highness, well...

200
00:12:40.720 --> 00:12:41.940
I'm sorry.

201
00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:47.890
Sorry for letting you down as well.

202
00:12:47.890 --> 00:12:49.940
N-No, I never...

203
00:12:50.520 --> 00:12:55.410
I'll try harder than ever 
before to endure the torture!

204
00:12:57.810 --> 00:12:58.700
Yes!

205
00:12:58.700 --> 00:13:00.230
I'll be rooting for you!

206
00:13:03.090 --> 00:13:05.930
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

207
00:13:06.470 --> 00:13:10.090
Princess, time for some torture!

208
00:13:08.140 --> 00:13:10.390
Beastmaster
Krall

209
00:13:10.550 --> 00:13:12.130
Krall-chan!

210
00:13:12.870 --> 00:13:14.640
Where's Hngy-Baby?

211
00:13:14.640 --> 00:13:16.210
He's keeping watch back home!

212
00:13:16.210 --> 00:13:18.560
Aw, I was hoping to see him again!

213
00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:19.260
For real?

214
00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:21.760
I mean, Hngy-Baby's adorable!

215
00:13:21.760 --> 00:13:22.930
I know, right?

216
00:13:22.930 --> 00:13:25.020
Hngy-Baby's totes adorbs!

217
00:13:25.250 --> 00:13:27.710
You should come hang out at my place!

218
00:13:27.710 --> 00:13:29.950
You can meet all the others, too!

219
00:13:29.950 --> 00:13:31.440
What, really?

220
00:13:31.440 --> 00:13:32.690
I'm totally down!

221
00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:34.270
Your Highness?

222
00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:34.270
Krall?

223
00:13:34.760 --> 00:13:37.790
That's right, Princess.
No more goofing around!

224
00:13:38.040 --> 00:13:41.980
Unlike last time, today's torture 
is totally the real deal!

225
00:13:41.980 --> 00:13:43.310
Prepare yourself!

226
00:13:43.900 --> 00:13:44.850
Come on in!

227
00:13:49.070 --> 00:13:49.960
That's...

228
00:13:53.690 --> 00:13:56.140
That's a good boy, Mad Wolf.

229
00:13:56.140 --> 00:13:59.150
Krall Regiment Combat Soldier

230
00:13:56.140 --> 00:13:59.150
Mad Wolf

231
00:13:59.690 --> 00:14:00.870
A mad wolf!

232
00:14:01.280 --> 00:14:03.060
Be careful, Your Highness!

233
00:14:03.060 --> 00:14:08.350
Wolves are known as the strongest of all monster
 families when it comes to pure fighting power!

234
00:14:09.290 --> 00:14:11.270
Have you forgotten, Ex?

235
00:14:11.270 --> 00:14:13.670
I've defeated wolves in the past.

236
00:14:14.670 --> 00:14:18.670
It wasn't an easy fight, but 
they're not unbeatable.

237
00:14:19.150 --> 00:14:24.210
However, mad wolves are a different 
beast altogether, even among wolves.

238
00:14:24.210 --> 00:14:27.950
They're twice as strong as the gran 
wolves you struggled to defeat.

239
00:14:27.950 --> 00:14:28.590
What?

240
00:14:28.590 --> 00:14:30.020
That's strong as hell!

241
00:14:30.020 --> 00:14:31.590
All right, Princess.

242
00:14:32.040 --> 00:14:33.840
Let's start the torture!

243
00:14:35.790 --> 00:14:37.960
What enormous, thick legs!

244
00:14:37.960 --> 00:14:39.600
If that thing lands a hit on you...

245
00:14:44.180 --> 00:14:49.250
Mad Wolf's allure lies in his 
big, cute paw pads for sure!

246
00:14:49.780 --> 00:14:50.870
Not to mention...

247
00:14:54.130 --> 00:14:57.650
Ah, it smells so nice!

248
00:14:57.650 --> 00:15:02.330
The unique scent of their paw pads!

249
00:15:02.330 --> 00:15:04.120
You can't beat it, baby!

250
00:15:05.250 --> 00:15:07.790
<i>That's so specific that 
I'm not jealous at all.</i>

251
00:15:07.790 --> 00:15:09.280
Okay, Princess!

252
00:15:09.280 --> 00:15:12.210
If you're dying of envy, then 
let's hear that secret!

253
00:15:12.210 --> 00:15:14.970
No, I'm not jealous.

254
00:15:16.050 --> 00:15:16.980
What?

255
00:15:17.280 --> 00:15:21.620
M-Mad wolf paw pads have a stronger 
scent than doggies or kitties do...

256
00:15:21.620 --> 00:15:24.270
I've never sniffed an animal's 
paw pads to begin with.

257
00:15:25.180 --> 00:15:26.230
No way!

258
00:15:26.230 --> 00:15:28.310
That's like missing out 
on half of life itself!

259
00:15:28.310 --> 00:15:30.330
Paw pads make up half of our lives now?

260
00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:32.930
Here, give it a whiff.

261
00:15:32.930 --> 00:15:34.150
What?

262
00:15:36.730 --> 00:15:37.790
Smells like animal funk.

263
00:15:37.790 --> 00:15:39.570
It's a nice smell!

264
00:15:39.570 --> 00:15:41.660
C'mon, try sniffing it again!

265
00:15:41.660 --> 00:15:42.870
Ugh, no thanks.

266
00:15:42.870 --> 00:15:43.800
Please!

267
00:15:43.800 --> 00:15:45.640
I'll let you in on my secret!

268
00:15:45.640 --> 00:15:47.210
How the tables have turned.

269
00:15:47.210 --> 00:15:48.310
What secret?

270
00:15:48.890 --> 00:15:52.880
The grand inquisitor has her newborn 
niece as her phone wallpaper!

271
00:15:52.880 --> 00:15:54.170
Hey, Krall!

272
00:15:54.170 --> 00:15:55.050
How do you know that?!

273
00:15:55.050 --> 00:15:57.520
Look, I shared my secret!

274
00:15:57.520 --> 00:15:58.770
What?

275
00:15:59.160 --> 00:16:02.840
Fine, I'll give it another whiff.

276
00:16:04.150 --> 00:16:06.490
W-Well?

277
00:16:07.670 --> 00:16:08.530
Ah!

278
00:16:08.530 --> 00:16:12.670
Underneath the animal funk, it 
smells a bit like popcorn...

279
00:16:12.670 --> 00:16:14.440
Yeah! Yeah!

280
00:16:16.270 --> 00:16:19.880
The pad itself feels so nice and squishy...

281
00:16:20.550 --> 00:16:21.520
<i>Huh?</i>

282
00:16:21.520 --> 00:16:23.950
<i>Ah, wait...</i>

283
00:16:24.730 --> 00:16:27.950
<i>I could get hooked on this!</i>

284
00:16:29.290 --> 00:16:30.460
Welcome.

285
00:16:31.150 --> 00:16:33.280
To the world of paw pads!

286
00:16:35.680 --> 00:16:37.930
The princess had her eyes
opened to a new world

287
00:16:39.590 --> 00:16:41.270
Thanks, Krall-cchi.

288
00:16:41.270 --> 00:16:44.550
For opening my eyes to a brand new world!

289
00:16:44.550 --> 00:16:50.170
Nah, I'm just glad you get the paw hype now!

290
00:16:50.570 --> 00:16:52.060
Oh, I know!

291
00:16:52.060 --> 00:16:55.080
Let's have a paw party back at my place!

292
00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:56.020
I'm down!

293
00:16:56.020 --> 00:16:57.500
Let's invite everyone else!

294
00:16:58.630 --> 00:17:01.010
How about it, Grand Inquisitor?

295
00:17:01.560 --> 00:17:03.620
I swear, you two...

296
00:17:05.280 --> 00:17:06.790
Will there be bunnies?

297
00:17:07.040 --> 00:17:09.240
You betcha, baby!

298
00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:11.720
<i>Ah, so cute...</i>

299
00:17:15.900 --> 00:17:17.410
Hngy-Baby!

300
00:17:17.410 --> 00:17:19.900
So warm and relaxing...

301
00:17:19.900 --> 00:17:21.360
How's it going?

302
00:17:21.360 --> 00:17:22.680
How's it going?

303
00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:24.430
Whoa, you're a clever one!

304
00:17:28.570 --> 00:17:29.970
What about the torture?

305
00:17:31.400 --> 00:17:35.400
'Tis Time for
"Torture," Princess

306
00:17:35.400 --> 00:17:38.410
Hellgrove Park

307
00:17:37.240 --> 00:17:38.410
Hurry up!

308
00:17:38.410 --> 00:17:39.890
I can't wait!

309
00:17:47.090 --> 00:17:50.060
It's time for torture, Princess!

310
00:17:49.790 --> 00:18:00.470
Hell-Lord's Daughter
Hyper Cadet Harm-Marshal
    Maomao-chan

311
00:17:50.670 --> 00:17:53.300
I really like playing at the park!

312
00:17:53.300 --> 00:17:56.710
So seeing me play should make you jealous!

313
00:17:57.030 --> 00:17:58.160
Just watch me!

314
00:17:58.160 --> 00:17:59.820
Yeah, I'm watching.

315
00:18:01.630 --> 00:18:03.140
Wait up!

316
00:18:09.680 --> 00:18:11.690
Careful, careful...

317
00:18:12.370 --> 00:18:13.940
So fast!

318
00:18:14.500 --> 00:18:17.440
Ah, so cute.

319
00:18:17.760 --> 00:18:19.530
Everything's cute about her.

320
00:18:19.530 --> 00:18:21.050
She really is so cute.

321
00:18:23.840 --> 00:18:26.350
She's gonna talk, isn't she?

322
00:18:26.350 --> 00:18:27.900
And join in on the fun.

323
00:18:28.490 --> 00:18:30.070
Don't worry, Ex.

324
00:18:30.920 --> 00:18:32.200
That won't happen.

325
00:18:33.070 --> 00:18:37.520
Maomao-chan may be cute, but that 
doesn't mean I want to join in.

326
00:18:38.010 --> 00:18:41.020
I've never liked parks very much.

327
00:18:41.020 --> 00:18:42.340
What do you mean?

328
00:18:43.160 --> 00:18:44.310
I was...

329
00:18:45.170 --> 00:18:48.840
forbidden from playing in 
parks when I was younger.

330
00:18:50.070 --> 00:18:53.010
Parks are not a place 
for royalty to play.

331
00:18:53.010 --> 00:18:56.140
That's the lesson I had 
deeply ingrained in me.

332
00:18:56.890 --> 00:18:58.030
Which is why...

333
00:18:58.610 --> 00:19:01.500
I don't feel the desire to play here at all!

334
00:19:01.500 --> 00:19:03.080
Magnificent, Your Highness!

335
00:19:03.340 --> 00:19:06.960
Princess and Commander of 
the Imperial Third Legion!

336
00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:11.510
You've fully taken those childhood 
royal lessons to heart!

337
00:19:13.100 --> 00:19:14.480
Of course.

338
00:19:14.480 --> 00:19:16.470
I've had to lead a distinguished 
life since birth.

339
00:19:16.830 --> 00:19:21.930
Even as a child... I-I understood this...

340
00:19:21.930 --> 00:19:23.090
Your Highness?

341
00:19:24.840 --> 00:19:27.640
Truth is, I wanted to play 
with everyone else...

342
00:19:27.640 --> 00:19:28.850
You gave in awfully fast!

343
00:19:29.220 --> 00:19:30.940
I wanted to play...

344
00:19:30.940 --> 00:19:32.970
And go on the seesaw...

345
00:19:31.230 --> 00:19:44.580
Giggle giggle

346
00:19:32.970 --> 00:19:35.660
And climb up the jungle gym...

347
00:19:34.440 --> 00:19:44.580
Smirk smirk

348
00:19:35.660 --> 00:19:38.180
And make castles in the sandbox...

349
00:19:35.730 --> 00:19:44.580
Yeah!

350
00:19:38.180 --> 00:19:40.610
Calm down, Your Highness.

351
00:19:40.610 --> 00:19:43.200
Don't let your own memories 
be your downfall.

352
00:19:44.880 --> 00:19:46.580
Missy!

353
00:19:47.580 --> 00:19:49.000
Maomao-chan!

354
00:19:50.960 --> 00:19:52.540
Let's play together!

355
00:19:54.190 --> 00:19:54.990
Sure!

356
00:19:54.990 --> 00:19:56.010
Your Highness?!

357
00:19:56.840 --> 00:19:59.300
The princess
confessed

358
00:19:59.470 --> 00:20:01.590
C'mon, missy!

359
00:20:01.590 --> 00:20:03.170
Not so fast!

360
00:20:02.680 --> 00:20:03.970
Hurry up!

361
00:21:04.810 --> 00:21:06.980
Man, that was fun!

362
00:21:06.980 --> 00:21:07.570
Yep!

363
00:21:07.570 --> 00:21:09.360
I played my heart out!

364
00:21:09.360 --> 00:21:10.280
We should hang out again!

365
00:21:10.280 --> 00:21:11.240
Yeah.

366
00:21:13.600 --> 00:21:16.830
What was the most fun part, Maomao-chan?

367
00:21:16.830 --> 00:21:17.640
Huh?

368
00:21:18.050 --> 00:21:19.660
Why do I need to pick?

369
00:21:21.630 --> 00:21:23.460
So everything was fun, then?

370
00:21:24.700 --> 00:21:25.760
Yeah!

371
00:21:26.360 --> 00:21:28.440
Everything was fun!

372
00:21:29.190 --> 00:21:30.360
Same for me!

373
00:21:40.270 --> 00:21:41.610
Your Majesty.

374
00:21:42.130 --> 00:21:45.330
The Royal Empire's security password 
we obtained from the princess.

375
00:21:45.770 --> 00:21:48.410
The Chief Officer of Combat 
was asking for it.

376
00:21:48.980 --> 00:21:53.170
Would you be so kind as to lend me 
the note with the password on it?

377
00:21:53.500 --> 00:21:55.600
Geh-heh-heh.

378
00:21:55.600 --> 00:21:57.410
That note, you say?

379
00:21:57.660 --> 00:22:02.020
The video filled with scenes 
of Maomao-chan playing.

380
00:22:02.020 --> 00:22:05.330
I was so engrossed in watching that...

381
00:22:04.940 --> 00:22:09.940
